@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nctyqc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v0
    v2 = ((v1 / v2) / (0.12 * wp.abs(v2 + 0.53)))
    v1 = (v0 * 0.54)
    tmp = v1
    v0 = ((0.45 * v2) + 0.14)
    data[tid] = v0
